{"tid":999861,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"娥特全程黑面　無跟議員握手","createTime":"2019-01-29T04:46:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-29T04:59:23.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"e67075599c893988d6d51745c7d5b7793f6f44f1","tid":999861,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T04:46:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190129/20601707\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190129%2F20601707&d=kLXyKWzv0KFRbXtH0eH7a7%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=6bc1cf4c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190129%2F20601707&h=5f014aa9\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190129/20601707</a><br />\n<br />\n2019年01月29日 <br />\n<br />\n娥特全程黑面　無跟議員握手<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190129/large/0128long2002.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190129%2Flarge%2F0128long2002.jpg&h=e8f78edb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n七名泛民議員昨晤林鄭後會見傳媒。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【特稿】特首林鄭月娥早前指民主派議員「妒忌」她與建制派見面討論長者綜援，引起民主派強烈不滿後，林鄭最終也在昨日親自見民主派，但有與會者形容會面氣氛並不理想，林鄭不單全程「黑面」，甚至連與出席會議議員握手也懶做。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：晤泛民不歡而散　林鄭拒檢討<br />\n<br />\n拒解釋「妒忌論」<br />\n<br />\n有與會民主派議員透露，昨與林鄭會面雖未再出現提早拉隊離場，但雙方會面氣氛並不理想。據了解，民主派議員早約五分鐘進入政總會議室，林鄭到場後並無與任何議員握手，出席會議時更全程「黑面」，而她到場入座後，即以時間有限為由，表明要「我（林鄭）講先」，又藉機反駁民主派指她只見建制派議員：「我想講大家聽，我唔淨係見建制派，我嗰日18號見完，20號就搭飛機」，並指自己周六返港後，已即時透過特首辦主任陳國基約見民主派。面對民主派議員林卓廷、葉建源就其「妒忌論」的質疑，據知林鄭只說：「你話我係直言好、失言又好，總之你要我解，我都答唔到點解」。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭會上亦強調自己認同羅致光就收緊長者綜援一事表述，明言：「我同意羅致光講嘅嘢。」<br />\n<br />\n最終民主派與林鄭會面50分鐘後，特首辦主任陳國基即以林鄭還有另一場活動為由，要結束會議。邵家臻會議尾聲時，曾問林鄭拒絕民主派全部建議，會後是否只能重申政府將於今年檢視特別津貼和補助金安排時，林鄭只攤大雙手說：「係囉」，雙方就不歡而散。<br />\n<br />\n■記者林俊謙  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n晤泛民不歡而散　林鄭拒檢討<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n領長生津者或可申領四千元<br />\n<br />\n晤泛民不歡而散　林鄭拒檢討<br />\n跨黨派譴責政府收緊長者綜援兩議員爆粗狂鬧羅致光"},{"pid":"925654febf4c0a05e6e45efc14a0ae510d023392","tid":999861,"uid":13592,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T04:46:53.000Z","msg":"有險可守呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec91db24b50010118d9441a7e761820bc571e75d","tid":999861,"uid":28309,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T04:48:04.000Z","msg":"當正自己老細咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n香港"},{"pid":"8264a3da61edcae273d2f855a70a16d1f1c420d4","tid":999861,"uid":155137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T04:48:36.000Z","msg":"泛民是<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6ba1172eae311d5ae74009f2b443e579edc4e29","tid":999861,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T04:51:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有險可守呀&lt;img src=&quot;/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif&quot; class=&quot;hkgmoji&quot; /&gt; &lt;img src=&quot;/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif&quot; class=&quot;hkgmoji&quot; /&gt; &lt;img src=&quot;/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif&quot; class=&quot;hkgmoji&quot; /&gt;</blockquote><br />\n殘而不廢"},{"pid":"ce899bc4c5c9c3b7d7ba122c7711981497ae6437","tid":999861,"uid":42804,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T04:52:19.000Z","msg":"777:「反正我點做，你地班友都會屌，不過你地有你地屌，我都照推，反正你地根本起唔到乜野作用，人都比我地多，同你地特登見面都係畀面你。」"},{"pid":"3ec5ffc787184c1488eddafa427ec3d82b70682a","tid":999861,"uid":42804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T04:53:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>777:「反正我點做，你地班友都會屌，不過你地有你地屌，我都照推，反正你地根本起唔到乜野作用，人都比我地<span style=\"color: red;\">少</span>，同你地特登見面都係畀面你。」</blockquote>"},{"pid":"c3f3dbf645ded4b89f58c8a2ad7344a2e22bbd9b","tid":999861,"uid":82482,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T04:54:42.000Z","msg":"你班飯民仲有利用價值咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbf7776dd6ac1f167f6de3043e3723a04f5eb001","tid":999861,"uid":9230,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T04:56:28.000Z","msg":"毛澤東都教過啦，別人反對我讚成，別人讚成我反對"},{"pid":"7f27f3a8ab5b2eb790eeb9e589505282cb4980e7","tid":999861,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T04:57:37.000Z","msg":"原本連見都唔想見你班仆街"},{"pid":"f90bf51f4c6ca098cee354d8095491d72955c5ae","tid":999861,"uid":42804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c3f3dbf645ded4b89f58c8a2ad7344a2e22bbd9b","tid":999861,"uid":82482,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T04:54:42.000Z","msg":"你班飯民仲有利用價值咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T04:58:18.000Z","msg":"以前都仲有少用，而家？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n人數已經少，分組點票又唔全部出席，自己人有事第一時間割蓆走人。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbca9174bb88a926e0000e01e6d05085366e5f6a","tid":999861,"uid":42804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fbf7776dd6ac1f167f6de3043e3723a04f5eb001","tid":999861,"uid":9230,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T04:56:28.000Z","msg":"毛澤東都教過啦，別人反對我讚成，別人讚成我反對"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T04:59:23.000Z","msg":"到分組點票會有人潛水。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}